            "title": "油價低收逾1%　美國推動俄烏達成和平協議或提振供應",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國際油價跌逾1%收市，創1個月低位，因美國推動俄烏達成和平協議，可能刺激全球石油供應。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/OIL-PRICE_FB_source-ap_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/OIL-PRICE_FB_source-ap_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油報每桶58.06美元，跌94美仙，跌幅近1.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油收市報每桶62.56美元，跌82美仙，跌幅近1.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英美期油本周累跌近3%或以上。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15446723-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6%e9%80%be1%e3%80%80%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e6%8e%a8%e5%8b%95%e4%bf%84%e7%83%8f%e9%81%94%e6%88%90%e5%92%8c%e5%b9%b3%e5%8d%94%e8%ad%b0%e6%88%96%e6%8f%90%e6%8c%af%e4%be%9b",
